Feature: US55: Disposal to Trade: Summary of disposal information presented to the Motor Trader
  As a Motor Trader
  I want to see a summary of the details relating to a vehicle that has been disposed before I submit a disposal
  So that I can confirm a submission of a disposal for a vehicle

  Scenario:
    Given that the user has entered all required information
    When the summary page has been reached
    Then the information entered is presented back to the motor trader